14. Bxc6+ bxc6 15. Bg3 { Black must castle now. } 15... O-O 16. Rb1 Qd4 17.
dxe7 Re8 18. Re1 Nd5 19. Be5
{ We keep gaining tempi thanks to the black queen. } 19... Qc5 20. Ba1
