19. Qh6 { It is important to start with this move since it stops Kg7. } 19...
a4 20. a3 { Stopping any kind of counterplay. } 20... Qf2 21. c5
{ Is an instructive resource for White. Opening the a2-g8 diagonal for the bishop. }
21... Qxc5 22. f4
{ The g-file will be opened which means game over for Black. } *

