11... Bxb5 12. fxe5 dxe3 13. exf6 e2+ 14. Kh1 exd1=Q 15. fxg7
{ The final touch is just amazing. } 15... Qg4 16. gxh8=Q Bxc4 17. Rf3
{ Although, Black has three@@StartBracket@@!@@EndBracket@@ pieces for the rook, he is lost. With Rg3 next, Black king has no safe squares. White will restore material balance and continue with deadly attack. }
