21. Qc3+ Bf6 22. Be5 { Things are very forced. } 22... Qxb5 23. Bxf6+ Nxf6 24.
Rxh8 { The capturing continues. } 24... Bb7 25. Rxa8 Bxa8 26. Qd3
{ Three passed pawns and rook should be much stronger than two pieces. } *

