20... O-O 21. f5 { Attack. } 21... e5 22. f6 { Not wasting time. } 22... Bd8
23. fxg7 Kxg7 24. Be3 a4 25. g6
{ And White is faster again.  25...fxg6  is impossible because of  26.Bh6+  and after  25...hxg6  White opens the h-file after  26.h5  . }
