exd5 Nxd5 13. Qa4 Nb4 14. O-O Be7 15. a3 Nxd3 16. Qxc6+ Kf8 17. Nb6 Ra7 18. Be3
{ Looks horrible for Black. He will have to play Nf4 at some point allowing White to take over the c-file. }
