9... Nxd5 10. exd5 { Black has to decide where to put his knight. } 10... Nd4
{ An Active move, but runs into c3 tempo. } 11. c3 Nf5
{ It is not clear what is the knight doing on f5 since black's main idea is usually to push the f-pawn. }
12. Nc2
{ I prefer to improve the knight instead of playing  12.c4  which might be also good enough for the advantage. }
