9. c4 Nf5 { The knight seems strange on f5 to my eyes. } 10. Bd3
{ Developing and targeting the knight. } 10... g6
{ Guarding the knight and preparing for bishop fianchetto. } 11. O-O a6
{ Black must chase the knight. } 12. Nc3 Bg7 13. Bxf5
