14. Be3 Rc8 15. Qa4+ Qd7
{ We were following the game P.Maghsoodloo - A.Fawzy, Sharjah 2021. } 16. Rac1
{ Indirectly defending the c4-pawn. } 16... Bd3
{ Doesn't win a pawn for Black. } 17. Qxd7+ Kxd7 18. Rfd1 Bxc4
{ Loses immediately. } 19. Na4 { Black can't stop material losses. } *

