Qc7
{ One or two decade@@StartBracket@@s@@EndBracket@@ ago computers were not so strong and some people still believed that it is possible to waste one tempo in such position and still have a decent game. Today, things are different, and the engines are already giving a winning advantage to White here. }
12. h4 { White's moves are simple. } 12... h5 13. g4 Rfc8
{ 13...hxg4?  14.h5  is disaster for Black. } 14. gxh5 Nxh5 15. Nb5
