1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 d6 6. Bg5 e6 7. Qd2 a6
{ Since we have seen that Black can't really get enough counterplay without a6-b5 plan it seems logical to start with this move. }
