10. Qxd4 Be7
{ Unlike h6 this is a must move for Black.   If  10...b5?  then  11.f4  and 12. e5 is unstoppable threat. }
11. f3 { According to plan. } 11... b5 12. g4
{ White wants to push g5 as fast as possible, which means his next move is Be3 followed by g5. }
12... O-O { 12...Qc7  14.Be3  and playing h6 won't stop g5 for too long. } 13.
Be3
