13... Bc6 { Black needs d7 square for the knight. } 14. h4 Nd7 15. h5 h6
{ Forced due to 16. h6 threat. } 16. Qd2 Ne5 17. Qg2
{ Defending f3, and putting queen on g-file is typical for Scheveningen. }
17... b4 18. Ne2 Nc4 19. Bc1
{ Black was trying something active, and he is running out of the moves. Now White will start dangerous attack. }
