20... Qh2 21. Bxe6+ Kh8 22. Qa4
{ Another double attack, White wins back the exchange. } 22... Rxc3 23. bxc3
Bxc3 24. Qc4 { The bishop has no squares to go to. } 24... Nf4
{ The only move which doesn't resign. } 25. Qxc3 Nxe6 26. Rd6
{ Material is equal, but White will pick up the pawn on e5, and Black still has big troubles on the last two ranks. }
