15... Bxd5 16. exd5 Nb6 17. Na5
{ The typical idea, the knight is heading towards the c6 square. } 17... Nxd5
{ Black should try instead  17...g6  or  17...Nf4  , but White keeps an edge there also. }
18. Qxd5 Qxa5 19. Bc4 { Nice trick which helps White to improve the bishop. }
19... Rf8 20. Bb3 { White is dominating on the light squares. } *

