{ However, White's bishops are too strong. } 21... Ra5 22. a4
{ This strong move destroys Black's hopes. The White king is completely safe now, and the pawn on a4 is an important resource in the endgame. White converted his advantage into the win in game Shankland - Duda, Prague 2021. }
