16... Rfe8 { I don't know what can Black do on the e-file. } 17. Rg1
{ Preparing g4. } 17... e4 18. Nc2 { The knight comes into play. } 18... Ne5
19. Nd4
{ The centralized knight and the bishop pair should give White a decent advantage. }
