15. Kxd2 Nxd5 16. exd5 Bd7 17. a4 Bb2 18. Rb1 Ba3
{ So far we have transposed to theMaroczy bind lines. } 19. h4
{ White misses an opportunity. The first new moment for us.   19.b4!  is mentioned in the course as close to winning for White. The black bishop is in big trouble. }
19... b5
